  "merge_notes": "All three cards are ICT school; no school conflict. The second card (Order of Reversal) had fewer identification rules and no related concepts; its content was subsumed. The third card provided the most complete definition and rules. Minor nuance: the first card listed FVG as a separate stage after CSD, while others treat FVG as optional; unified card treats FVG as optional later stage.",
